

The 3rd version of ppz site. All contents are static pages plus JavaScript code,
which can be served by light weight http servers, such as lighttpd.

To update the site contents, edit the files under the following dirs:

./poems
./photos

Edit the # in js/photo.js

PSY index files are copied from the corpus project's psy_index_json dir to:

./psy_index_json

To deploy the site for debugging:

./deploy.py ~/www/ppz

Or, to finalize and deploy the site with compiled JavaScript code:

./deploy.py ~/www/ppz opt
